{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef68af2c6a","title":"印发河南省委关于农村人民公社整社算账工作的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e7900a4247","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":10,"articleId":"ef68af2c6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"87da8bef02","type":"title","text":"印发河南省委关于农村人民公社整社算账工作的报告“的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a"},{"id":"1b2df349a4","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志参考。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a"},{"id":"bf9c512733","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a"},{"id":"bbc5732cd6","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a"},{"id":"0d7c25972b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中共河南省委1959年6月22日给中央并各地、市、县委的这一报告说，我省整社算账工作已经在麦收前基本上胜利结束。整个算账运动的发展是健康的、迅速的，始终实行了算账与生产相结合，加强领导与发动群众相结合，算清经济账与解决干部思想作风相结合，边清算边兑现，边鸣放边整改，不仅算清了经济方面的账目，同时也解决了干部思想作风上的问题，揭露出了不少环分子。经过整社算账，整个农村已经发生了极为深刻的变化，呈现了莲莲勃勃的新气象，出现了新的生产高潮。当前的任务是进一步巩固和扩大整社成果，结合生产解决遗留问题。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a"}],"page":{"id":"3fbd501d72","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"ef68af2c6a","start":178,"end":178}}}},"__N_SSG":true}